### Chat Endpoint - Basic Request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "16的平方根是多少？"
}

### Chat Endpoint - With Conversation ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "请记住我的名字是张三",
    "conversationId": "conv-001"
}

### Clear Specific Conversation
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chat/clear/conv-001

### Clear All Conversations
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chat/clear-all

### Get All Conversations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations

### Get Conversation Message Count
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations/conv-001/count

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health/service

### ==================== Document Management Endpoints ====================

### Upload Documents
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "texts": [
        "Spring AI 是一个用于构建 AI 应用的 Spring 框架扩展。",
        "PostgreSQL 是一个强大的开源关系型数据库。",
        "pgvector 是 PostgreSQL 的向量相似度搜索扩展。"
    ],
    "metadata": {
        "source": "manual_upload",
        "category": "technology"
    }
}

### Search Documents
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/documents/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "数据库",
    "topK": 5,
    "threshold": 0.0
}

### Search Documents with Filter
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/documents/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "Spring",
    "topK": 10,
    "threshold": 0.5,
    "filterExpression": "category == 'technology'"
}

### Delete Documents
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/documents
Content-Type: application/json

["document-id-1", "document-id-2"]